"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Kaplan-Meier analysis of the percentage of patients maintaining a therapeutic rate control response to each dose level of intravenous diltiazem infusion in patients who initially responded to bolus diltiazem. Maintenance of rate control was greater at doses of 10 to 15 mg/h.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
